80
00:03:48,311 --> 00:03:48,950
my faith

81
00:03:48,950 --> 00:03:50,790
in justice will completely collapse.

82
00:03:52,551 --> 00:03:54,190
When we caused trouble before,

83
00:03:54,190 --> 00:03:55,991
