92
00:04:21,271 --> 00:04:22,071
Step one,

93
00:04:22,631 --> 00:04:23,711
at 2 AM,

94
00:04:23,990 --> 00:04:25,751
leak info when everyone's asleep.

95
00:04:25,910 --> 00:04:27,790
This prevents Jun An
from reacting in time.

96
00:04:28,350 --> 00:04:29,071
Step two,

97
00:04:29,430 --> 00:04:31,550
deliberately plant
opposing paid commenters

98
00:04:31,550 --> 00:04:32,591
to argue in the comments.

99
00:04:32,910 --> 00:04:35,071
One side calls Ms. Bai a killer lawyer.

100
00:04:35,631 --> 00:04:37,391
The other says online information

101
00:04:37,470 --> 00:04:38,550
is 80% rumor.

102
00:04:38,550 --> 00:04:39,910
Just for attention and traffic.

103
00:04:40,350 --> 00:04:41,071
Step three,

104
00:04:41,910 --> 00:04:43,031
show evidence when dissed.

105
00:04:43,870 --> 00:04:45,031
Release round two.

106
00:04:45,350 --> 00:04:46,391
Based on my years

107
00:04:46,391 --> 00:04:47,990
of internet surfing experience,

108
00:04:48,790 --> 00:04:49,751
there's only one truth.

109
00:04:52,831 --> 00:04:53,352
What?

110
00:04:54,430 --> 00:04:56,031
Someone's deliberately setting this up.

111
00:04:56,430 --> 00:04:57,550
Targeting Ms. Bai.

112
00:04:59,951 --> 00:05:01,191
But why?

113
00:05:04,071 --> 00:05:04,910
Whatever the reason,

114
00:05:05,271 --> 00:05:05,790
anyway,

115
00:05:05,990 --> 00:05:06,751
I think we should

116
00:05:06,751 --> 00:05:07,751
report our suspicions

117
00:05:07,751 --> 00:05:08,511
to the firm.

118
00:05:08,631 --> 00:05:10,071
We can't let Ms. Bai be bullied.

119
00:05:19,591 --> 00:05:20,136
Ms. Bai.

120
00:05:22,271 --> 00:05:22,888
Ms. Bai.

121
00:05:24,391 --> 00:05:26,631
We're investigating who's behind this.

122
00:05:27,790 --> 00:05:28,391
Ms. Bai.

123
00:05:28,391 --> 00:05:29,591
I checked some IP addresses.

124
00:05:29,591 --> 00:05:30,591
No discernible pattern.

125
00:05:30,990 --> 00:05:32,990
I've submitted
a complaint to the website,

126
00:05:33,071 --> 00:05:34,470
demanding removal of the video

127
00:05:34,470 --> 00:05:35,910
and banning the main accounts.

128
00:05:36,230 --> 00:05:37,310
Please authorize me.

129
00:05:37,790 --> 00:05:38,408
May I?

130
00:05:38,990 --> 00:05:39,624
Sure.

131
00:05:40,230 --> 00:05:40,951
Thank you.

132
00:05:41,670 --> 00:05:42,310
But

133
00:05:42,310 --> 00:05:43,790
don't let this interfere with

134
00:05:43,790 --> 00:05:44,511
your real work.

135
00:05:46,230 --> 00:05:48,550
Should we just sit back and do nothing,

136
00:05:48,670 --> 00:05:51,310
and let them keep spreading
lies and slandering you?

137
00:05:52,550 --> 00:05:53,391
Twisting the truth,

138
00:05:53,550 --> 00:05:54,310
no principles,

139
00:05:54,751 --> 00:05:55,550
only after profit,

140
00:05:55,591 --> 00:05:56,391
acting unreasonably,

141
00:05:56,511 --> 00:05:57,230
aiding the wicked,

142
00:05:57,470 --> 00:05:58,711
double-dipping...

143
00:05:59,511 --> 00:06:01,031
In all my years as a lawyer,

144
00:06:01,391 --> 00:06:02,870
I've heard insults

145
00:06:03,271 --> 00:06:04,550
like these and more.

146
00:06:04,951 --> 00:06:06,350
If I broke down crying

147
00:06:06,350 --> 00:06:07,391
just because of these,

148
00:06:07,550 --> 00:06:08,470
neglected my real work,

149
00:06:08,470 --> 00:06:09,951
