drink coffee, never tea.

162
00:07:03,910 --> 00:07:04,790
Back in college,

163
00:07:04,790 --> 00:07:06,151
you always teased me

164
00:07:06,230 --> 00:07:07,350
about my old-man hobby.

165
00:07:08,191 --> 00:07:10,711
Earlier, I overheard Xiaoyu
complaining in the pantry.

166
00:07:11,310 --> 00:07:12,071
She said

167
00:07:12,071 --> 00:07:13,751
her exhausting work

168
00:07:14,591 --> 00:07:16,511
